                <h4>Domain - Complementary Courses (36 credits)</h4>

    
              <p>36 credits of complementary courses are selected as follows:</p>
<p>12 credits - Fundamentals<br />
3 credits - Basic Environmental Science<br />
6 credits - Statistics, one of two options<br />
15 credits - List 1 and List 2</p>
    
      
      
